reviewText: Examples seems to be improvised, some ideas are not well concluded ("it is just because"), the speaker needs to use non offensive language and it looks like the speaker does not have to much motivation.
Considero que los temas presentados, aunque son importantes, son bastante básicos. El moderador maneja un tono monótono que dificulta el engancharse a la exposición.
El material es muy bueno pero el ponente es un aburrido y tedioso de observar
Si bien se indican las diferentes herramientas mas conocidas para resolucion de problemas, la verdad esperaba un nivel más avanzado, con mayor enfasis en aplicaciones tecnicas en la industria.

Hubiera sido genial que se puedan dar los exámenes, y ya el pago por el certificado aparte. - It will be really great that you can make the quizz and get your results without paying, because you will not get the verified certify.

The speaker isn't very good, he speaks looking at his monitor all the time while he is reading the slides. I am not very happy about this course, I think it could be better if subjects would be deeper.
